title: Manowar - The Lord Of Steel Remastered
description:
Hail, Brothers & Sisters Of Steel!

It is one year ago, since Manowar released their "Lord Of Steel" Album. 
First, we had a shitty "Hammer Edition" - then we got a little bit better, but still shitty "Album"-Version. 

We all were wondering, why the "new" Manowar-Sound sounds so shitty. You, Me, we all do not know, why their sound sucks. However, live our favourite Band still sounds great. 


Today I present you a great, new,fanmade project - This is THE LORD OF STEEL - SWORD OF STEEL EDITION. It's a remastered Version of the Vinyl-Version of the album. 


THIS is the sound, how Manowar should sound. THIS is, how The Lord Of Steel should sound. 


Get it now - spread the message! THIS IS MANOWAR!

-------------------------------------------------------------

The Lord Of Steel - Sword Of Steel Edition - Remastered
MP3 - 320 kBit/s
New Cover included

ENJOY & SHARE! FUCK THE WORLD - HAIL & KILL !!
